{
  "texts": [
    "The real-world dataset is needed to test the real potential of the proposed method.",
    "Early detection of skin cancer allows for efficient treatment and prevention.",
    "Multiple DL methods have been reported for successfully identifying skin cancer.",
    "Unfortunately, these models are still ineffective at classifying cancer due to the shortage of images representing dangerous skin lesions.",
    "The studies illustrated that with deep learning image analysis, healthcare professionals can more accurately diagnose skin cancer using dermoscopy images."
  ]
}